title: Bug 19458[Navigator] Copy Project dialog UI problems
description: Bug 19458[Navigator] Copy Project dialog UI problems. The issue is with the red text in the dialog.
OB: When choosing the project name as 'test', a static text validation error appears on the dialog, highlighted in red.
EB: No static text validation error should be displayed when selecting the project name as 'test'. The dialog should function without UI problems.
SR:
1. Open the Copy Project dialog in the Navigator.
2. Choose the project name as 'test'.
3. Observe the appearance of a static text validation error in red on the dialog.
